1
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:41,120
Sawadee ka.

2
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:43,280
Gentlemen,

3
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,460
would you like female masseuses?

4
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:46,560
Sure.

5
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:47,520
Female masseuses?

6
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:47,960
No.

7
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:50,500
Do you have male masseurs?

8
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:53,000
I'd like one

9
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:54,600
with good technique,

10
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:56,480
someone who uses more pressure.

11
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,880
We have one available right now.

12
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,360
Do you mind if it's a male masseur?

13
00:00:59,360 --> 00:00:59,880
A male masseur?

14
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:00,440
I don't mind.

15
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:01,760
A male masseur is definitely a no.

16
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:03,280
Do you have any female ones?

17
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:05,040
What's wrong with male masseurs?

18
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,640
As long as they're good at it,

19
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:07,320
right?

20
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,200
Superficial.

21
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,570
Never mind them.

22
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,610
I'll take the male masseur.

23
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,400
Hello.

24
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,440
Could you start with my neck and shoulders?

25
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:30,320
My left shoulder hurts more.

26
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,320
You can press harder.

27
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,729
That is quite a bit of pressure.

28
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:42,100
Could you go down a little?

29
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:45,940
You can press even harder.

30
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:48,560
What...

31
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:51,280
Chen Angwei,

32
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:53,720
why are you here?

33
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,440
What?

34
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:57,970
Did you really want it to be that male masseur?

35
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,880
How is it? How's my pressure?

36
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,970
You're not a professional.

37
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:06,720
Professionals don't know you as well as I do.

38
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:07,880
Your left side is stiff

39
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:10,940
because you always tilt your head when doing homework.

40
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,800
You hate the pain of stretching

41
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:15,040
but like a strong, sore feeling.

42
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,640
I know all of this.

43
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,600
Go back now.

44
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,440
The masseur might come and see you.

45
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:25,240
It's fine. I talked to them.

46
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:27,360
What about Ou Shaowen?

47
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,160
He's getting his massage.

48
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,340
I told him I was going to the restroom.

49
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,760
But I think with your skills,

50
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,920
you could actually work here.

51
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,040
Of course.

52
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,320
I could consider it,

53
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:47,440
but the pay is a bit low.

54
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,880
The pay is low?

55
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,240
Why?

56
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:53,180
I'd only be making money from you.

57
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,960
I wouldn't pay you.

58
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,450
You want a free massage?

59
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,900
Then I'm going to stretch you.

60
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:01,980
Angwei,

61
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,200
the masseur has been here for a while. Are you coming?

62
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,460
I'm making money here.

63
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,800
What are you doing?

64
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,860
What are you doing?

65
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:13,620
Get out.

66
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,480
Just go.

67
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,200
Dailing.

68
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,120
So annoying.

69
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,480
Let me out.

70
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:51,850
I'm not sure if Uncle Danpa will still try to kill you.

71
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,320
It's safest for you to stay here.

72
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,440
I'm the only one who can protect you.

73
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,120
I don't need your protection at all.

74
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:02,680
Being near you

75
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,520
makes me sick.

76
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:07,560
Sick?

77
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:12,420
Being sick is better than being dead.

78
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,400
You just stay put.

79
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,010
I'm telling you,

80
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,079
don't even think about leaving.

81
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,640
My people are all around here.

82
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,760
You can't escape.

83
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,920
I got what I wanted.

84
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,560
What did I do wrong?

85
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,040
To get what you want,

86
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:34,080
you collude with those wicked people.

87
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,890
When did you become so despicable?

88
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,680
Everything about you now

89
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,680
disgusts me.

90
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,120
Only when I'm in a high position

91
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,180
can we protect you.

92
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:49,720
We?

93
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,250
What do you mean?

94
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,880
Of course I mean me

95
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,960
and the Siam Group behind me.

96
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,480
Just stay put.

97
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,920
I will send you whatever you need.

98
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:10,640
Take her away.

99
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,440
Yes.

100
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,280
Stay away from me.

101
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,920
I feel something is wrong.

102
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,480
Where is Dailing?

103
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:50,420
Ang Wei.

104
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,240
You're just a stray dog now.

105
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,880
What right do you have to negotiate with me?

106
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,800
Get out of here!

107
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,760
Today,

108
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,520
I must take Dailing with me.

109
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,740
I'll give you one more chance.

110
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,600
Get out.

111
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,200
Bury his body.

112
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,840
Don't dirty my yard.

113
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,480
See that?

114
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:52,440
Love is worth nothing.

115
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,240
This is what he gets.

116
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,040
Take her away.

117
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,360
I will definitely kill you.

118
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,720
You are really ruthless.

119
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,090
You wanted him dead more than I did.

120
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,360
He stole my woman,

121
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,620
and betrayed you, Godfather.

122
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,360
He is your enemy,

123
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,760
and even more so mine.

124
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,360
Now that he's dead,

125
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,400
what are your plans next?

126
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,680
Haven't I always told you

127
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,480
that I would help you take Mancheng?

128
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,400
Why not let Siam Group

129
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,330
merge with Sihai Group?

130
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,159
Merge?

131
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:53,200
I'll hand Siam Group over to you.

132
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:56,010
You'll be in charge, and I'll be the proxy.

133
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:59,120
Then the whole Mancheng will be yours.

134
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,520
How about it,

135
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:03,640
Godfather?

136
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,800
You're an interesting kid.

137
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,080
I knew I was right about you.

138
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,640
Without further ado.

139
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:14,840
Then tomorrow night.

140
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,240
Okay.

141
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:37,880
The two groups have been fighting for years.

142
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,210
Division brings chaos,

143
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,169
while unity brings wealth.

144
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:43,000
We are all in it for the money.

145
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:44,880
Today,

146
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,760
the two groups merge.

147
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:48,960
I have decided

148
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:52,560
that Ou Shaowen will manage the affairs of both.

149
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,520
I don't think so.

150
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,480
Danpa.

151
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,800
Ang Wei.

152
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,920
Weren't you shot?

153
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,040
Why are you here?

154
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,040
Danpa.

155
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,480
You killed my mother

156
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,120
and Dailing's parents.

157
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,440
You're not dead yet.

158
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,680
How could I die?

159
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:33,840
Shaowen,

160
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,250
what's going on?

161
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,240
Ang Wei.

162
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,040
Why are you so hard to kill?

163
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,360
Why do you think,

164
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:49,720
Uncle Danpa?
